{"tid":2102884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚鍵盤戰士] 藍屍空姐牛肉飯享特權 違法嚮facebook上載法庭相","createTime":"2020-07-10T22:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T15:36:07.000Z","uid":123774,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b9693ec261a5dc3a73e4c71fe90d699ea3f3ad7b","tid":2102884,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T22:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qFUfia.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qFUfia.png&h=e3361945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家delete左張相右邊3號庭張相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3fQx5r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3fQx5r.png&h=c7bb6c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJ5Qyby.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJ5Qyby.png&h=ee19146f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然Facebook唔會回應政府查詢<br />\n但<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>法庭睇返CCTV應該可以搵到佢影相</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n留意法庭係有寫明大樓內都唔可以影相<br />\n2017年唐琳玲嚮梁天琦審訊時偷拍<br />\n結果佢被判藐視法庭罪 監禁7日<br />\n<br />\n司法機構指出為咗保護法庭使用者安全<br />\n&ldquo;一般而言 法庭內不准攝影<br />\n至於<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>法院大樓的其他公眾範圍<br />\n只有獲得特別許可才可攝影</strong></span></span>&rdquo;<br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/law_order/html/2017/03/20170331_200416.lin.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcategories%2Flaw_order%2Fhtml%2F2017%2F03%2F20170331_200416.lin.shtml&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=2f483c5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/law_order/html/2017/03/20170331_200416.lin.shtml</a>)<br />\n<br />\n傳媒亦都唔會獲得特別優待<br />\n如有發現違規 將轉介警方跟誰<br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士 呢d低成本行動<br />\n你唔係唔幫手嘛?<br />\n咁做另一個目的係阻止藍屍影庭內手足!!<br />\n<br />\n唔想報狗就直接投訴去法庭: complaints@judiciary.hk<br />\n唔介意直接報狗: <a href=\"https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/CCC/PolicePublicPage?language=ch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FCCC%2FPolicePublicPage%3Flanguage%3Dch&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=ee148420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/CCC/PolicePublicPage?language=ch</a><br />\n<br />\n立場都有報導到:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%B6%E6%A6%AE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E7%94%B3%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E5%86%8D%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E9%A3%AF-%E6%9D%B1%E4%B8%BB-%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%2586%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E-%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25A7%2590%25E7%2589%259B%25E8%2582%2589%25E9%25A3%25AF-%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E7%25A9%258D%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=29f198aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%2586%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E-%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25A7%2590%25E7%2589%259B%25E8%2582%2589%25E9%25A3%25AF-%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E7%25A9%258D%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&h=876c7e69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%B6%E6%A6%AE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E7%94%B3%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E5%8